''See also [[resume]], [[resumé]]''
==English==
===Etymology===
From {{F.}} ''[[résumé#French|résumé]]'', past participle of ''[[résumer#French|résumer]]'', to summarize, from {{L.}} ''[[resumere]]'', to take back; compare '''[[resume]]'''

====Alternative spellings====
*[[resume]], [[resumé]]

